title: Not Time's Fool
description: Supernatural Fanfic - Sam/DeanA story in 21 parts, featuring an Ancient Greek curse, an unexpected metamorphosis, adventures in pool sharking, numerous shots of tequila, a nun outfit, zombies, angels, demons, kidnappings, startling discoveries about old acquaintances, massage, a game of strip poker, girl-on-girl action, girl-on-boy action, and boy-on-boy action. Despite my expectations or inclinations, it swiftly became clear that this story was going to be Sam/Dean. And, indeed, it is. Because my muse likes to fuck with me.It also features Girl!Dean - but don't let that put you off. It's still Dean, bless him, despite the sudden girlsuit.Wincest, 60243 Words - COMPLETECover by Dreamer with art by Itachei & eskatoad
author: FayJay
